Description:
Description
Possibility to Kopie Assistentie into Melding Mensenhandel.

Solution
Add in Assistentie Melding a button called 'Mensenhandel/Mensensmokkel'.
When this information is selected the following information should be copied:

Incident (number) - Assistentie number-Eventnumber
Adres van incident
Adres # van incident
Incident
Datum Melding
Tijd Melding
Aangewezen aan
Mutatie
(assistentie should be saved and everything should remain the same).
This information copied should create automatically a new record in Generiek - Melding.
Type Melding should be Assistentie
Naam Melder should be the user that created the Assistentie
Wekzaam bij should be organisation of this user
Datum should be same as when button Mensenhandel/Mensensmokkel is selected
Status is automatically in Behandeling.
The copied information should be added in the Omschrijving field.

Testplan
Step 1: Generiek - Assistentie - add a new assistentie
Step 2: Fill in mandatory fields and save.
Step 3: Edit existing record and select button Mensenhandel/Mensensmokkel and click save
Step 4: Go to Melding Mensenhandel - the information entered in the assistentie should be visible here.

Navigation
Generiek - Assistentie - Nieuw assistentie
Intake - Calltaker
Also Generiek Melding Mensenhandel
Select drop down from the list :: COMERCIELE INSTELLING
Click on Aangewezen aan auto search titles
